Description_lang: Launches a bolt of void energy at a player, inflicting $s1 Shadow damage within $A1 yds of the target and increasing threat generation by $s2% for $d. This bolt inflicts less damage the further away the target is. Upon expiration, transforms the target into an Agent of Demise.
AuraDescription_lang: Threat generation increased by $s2%.Upon expiration, transforms into an Agent of Demise.
